==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: (The sounds of) broad swords, and wide axes (as when an army sweeps through in battle).

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà dāo kuò fŭ

===Idiom===
'''[[大刀]][[闊]][[斧]]'''

# To handle something with daring and resolve; to be bold and decisive when handling an issue.

#: ''[[南京]][[市]][[將]]'''大刀闊斧'''[[地]][[對]][[延續]][[幾]][[十]][[年]][[的]][[行政]][[審批]][[制度]][[進行]][[全面]][[改革]].''

===Alternate forms===
